snippet.description:

https://www.smwcentral.net/?p=viewthread&t=125094

~omh~ is a 2023 yumplike SMW Mod Collab created by Team JANK lead by me aiming to emulate the original yump along with some influence by the VIP collabs. It serves as the missing chapter and the other side of R-ACK.
